   Piqueras, Monica, Hlth Res Inst La Fe IISLAFE, Resp Infect, Valencia, Spain.
   Domingo-Valero, Diana; Claramunt-Carbonell, Teresa, La Fe Univ \& Polytech Hosp, Cardiol Dept, Avinguda Fernando Abril Martorell 106, Valencia 46026, Spain.
   Domingo-Valero, Diana; Martinez-Dolz, Luis, Hlth Res Inst Hosp La Fe IISLaFe, Valencia, Spain.
