   Svensson, Siri Flogstad; Emblem, Kyrre E., Oslo Univ Hosp, Dept Phys \& Computat Radiol, Div Radiol \& Nucl Med, Oslo, Norway.
   Mireles, Eduardo Erasmo Mendoza; Vik-Mo, Einar Osland, Oslo Univ Hosp, Dept Neurosurg, Vilhelm Magnus Lab, Oslo, Norway.
