   Roberts, Amanda J., Scripps Res Inst, Anim Models Core Facil, La Jolla, CA 92037 USA.
   Teav, Tony; Borreggine, Rebecca; Kyritsi, Ioana; Gallart-Ayala, Hector; Ivanisevic, Julijana, Univ Lausanne, Fac Biol \& Med, Metabol \& Lipid Platform, CH-1015 Lausanne, Switzerland.
