Affiliation = {Mast, FD (Corresponding Author), Seattle Childrens Res Inst, Ctr Global Infect Dis Res, Seattle, WA 98145 USA.
   Bourgeois, Natasha M.; Bell, Satchel W.; Olivier, Jean Paul; Aitchison, John D.; Mast, Fred D., Seattle Childrens Res Inst, Ctr Global Infect Dis Res, Seattle, WA 98145 USA.
