   Galapon, Arthur; Brouwer, Charlotte L., Univ Groningen, Univ Med Ctr Groningen, Dept Radiat Oncol, Groningen, Netherlands.
   Cardenas, Carlos E., Univ Alabama Birmingham, Dept Radiat Oncol, Birmingham, AL USA.
   Fusella, Marco, Policlin Abano Terme, Radiat Oncol Dept, Abano Terme, Italy.
   Herbin, Geoffroy, Ion Beam Applicat, Louvain La Neuve, Belgium.
   Hurkmans, Coen, Catharina Hosp, Dept Radiat Oncol, Eindhoven, Netherlands.
