   Finni, Taija; Cronin, Neil, Univ Jyvaskyla, Fac Sport \& Hlth Sci, Jyvaskyla, Finland.
   Seynnes, Olivier, Norwegian Sch Sport Sci, Dept Phys Performance, Oslo, Norway.
