   Lindsey, Merry L.; Shivam, Pushkar; Nde, Pius N.; Curci, John A., Meharry Med Coll, Dept Biomed Sci, Nashville, TN 37208 USA.
   Lindsey, Merry L.; Curci, John A., Nashville Vet Affairs Med Ctr, Res Serv, Nashville, TN 37212 USA.
   Chen, Emily I.; Horn, David; Renuse, Santosh; Hakimi, Amirmansoor, Thermo Fisher Sci, San Jose, CA USA.
   Baxter, B. Timothy, Univ Nebraska Med Ctr, Dept Vasc Surg, Omaha, NE USA.
   Terrin, Michael, Univ Maryland, Sch Med, Dept Epidemiol \& Publ Hlth, Baltimore, MD USA.
   Matsumura, Jon S., Univ Colorado, Sch Med, Div Vasc Surg, Aurora, CO USA.
   Gaye, Amadou, Meharry Med Coll, Dept Integrat Genom \& Epidemiol, Nashville, TN USA.
   Curci, John A., Vanderbilt Univ, Sch Med, Dept Vasc Surg, Nashville, TN 37235 USA.},
