   Yi, WJ; Heo, MS (Corresponding Author), Seoul Natl Univ, Dent Res Inst, 101 Daehak Ro, Seoul 03080, South Korea.
   Oliveira, Matheus L.; Sampaio-Oliveira, Matheus; Freitas, Deborah Queiroz; Haiter-Neto, Francisco, Univ Estadual Campinas, Piracicaba Dent Sch, Dept Oral Diag, Piracicaba, SP, Brazil.
   Yang, Su, Houston Methodist Res Inst, Dept Oral \& Maxillofacial Surg, Houston, TX USA.
