   outcomes and incorporates a sensitivity-analysis perspective to assess
   ranking robustness under variations in criterion weights. The proposed
   framework establishes a transparent and adaptable decision-theoretic
   foundation for context-aware communication protocol selection in
   heterogeneous M2M scenarios.},
