   Batablinle, Lamboni; Yessou-Gnouyarou, Kassiki; Latevi, Lawson; Lorimpo, Kpengou; Zakari, M. Djibibe Moussa; Bannaa, Magolmeena, Univ Lome, Lab Solar Energy, Lome, Togo.
   Bazyomo, Serge, Univ Ouagadougou, Lab Energies Therm \& Renouvelables, Ouagadougou, Burkina Faso.
   Esso-ehanam, Tchedre Kpeli, Univ Joseph KI ZERBO, Dept Phys, Unit Training \& Res Exact \& Appl Sci, Lab Thermal \& Renewable Energies, BP 7021, Ouagadougou, Burkina Faso.},
DOI = {10.61435/ijred.2026.61680},
Keywords = {Togo; wind energy potential; seasonal variability; MERRA-2;
   CORDEX-Africa; regional climate models},
