   Kan, Hung-Cheng; Lin, Po-Hung; Shao, I. -Hung; Yu, Kai-Jie; Pang, See-Tong; Wu, Chun-Te, Chang Gung Univ, Coll Med, Taoyuan, Taiwan.
   Fan, Geng-Ming, Keelung Chang Geng Mem Hosp, Chang Geng Med Fdn, Dept Gen Med, Keelung, Taiwan.
