   Naser, Abdulqader Ghaleb, Tikrit Univ, Fac Agr, Dept Agr Machinery \& Equipment, Tikrit 34001, Iraq.
   Naser, Abdulqader Ghaleb; Nawi, Nazmi Mat; Kassim, Muhamad Saufi Mohd, Univ Putra Malaysia, Fac Engn, Dept Biol \& Agr Engn, Serdang 43400, Malaysia.
   Nawi, Nazmi Mat; Zakaria, Mohd Rafein; Kassim, Muhamad Saufi Mohd, Univ Putra Malaysia, Inst Plantat Studies, Serdang 43400, Malaysia.
   Zakaria, Mohd Rafein, Univ Putra Malaysia, Fac Biotechnol \& Biomol Sci, Dept Bioproc Technol, Serdang 43400, Malaysia.
