   Aydin, Roland C., Hamburg Univ Technol, Inst Continuum \& Mat Mech, Hamburg, Germany.
   Aydin, Roland C., Helmholtz Zentrum Hereon, Inst Mat Syst Modeling, Geesthacht, Germany.
   Hilgers, Ralf-Dieter, Rhein Westfal TH Aachen, Dept Med Stat, Aachen, Germany.},
