   Sanivarapu, Hemalatha; Kalenahalli, Yogendra, Int Crops Res Inst Semi Arid Trop, Cell \& Mol Biol \& Trait Engn, Hyderabad, India.
   Jagdish, Jaba, Int Crops Res Inst Semi Arid Trop, Crop Protect \& Seed Hlth Cluster, Hyderabad, India.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.ijbiomac.2025.148741},
EarlyAccessDate = {NOV 2025},
